{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "KUNGS/ mahzi man\nnannu Gallu/ un to Mehru\nmanno Deeno/ kahds tas irr/ ka\nes finnu/ ka nihkams es efmu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Redsi/ tu efi mannas\nDeenas Plaukstes Plattumu\nizzis/ un mans Muhſch irr ka\neneeka preeſch tewim/ tee-\nſchan/ iſkatrs Zilweks irr wiﬀai\nNeleetiba/ ir paſcha Stipruma/\nSela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Zilweks ta patt stat-\na ka Ehná/ un padarra few\ndauds weltigas Raises/ gann\nwiſch ſakrahj/ bet ne finna/\nkas to dabbuhs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nu tad/ us ko buhs man\naidiht KUNGS? es zerreju us\newi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Isglahb mannis no wiſ-\nahin mannahm Pahrkahpscha-\nnahm/ un ne leeſ man Gekkeim\npar Apfineekli tapt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es palikſchu tihri kluffu/\nin ne atdarrischu faru Mutti/\ntu gann padarrisi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atxemim tawu Mohzibu\nno mannim/ jo es efmu pamir-\nris no tawas Rohfas Gruhtu-\nma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad tu kurren pahrmahzi\npar teemi Noseegumeem/ tad is-\nnihzina tu winna Skaistumu ta\nka Rohdas/ ak! teecham/ wiſi\nZilweki irr Neleetiba/ Sela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Klaust/ KUNGS/ man-\nnu Luhgschann/ atgreeſ Ausis\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "pee mannas Kleegschanas/ un ne\nzeeti kluffu pahr mannahm Af-\nsarahm/ jo es efmu pee tew par w\nSweschineeku un Namneeku/ itt\nka wiſti manni Tehwi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Atstahjeeß no mannim/\nka es atspirgstohs/ pirms es no-\neemu/ un wairs ne buhſchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XL. Dseefma.\nIrr weena krahschna Papreekschfluddinaschana\nno Kristus/ un winna Zeeſchanas un Mir-\nſchanas: 2. Ka wiſch ar teem Lewitifteem\nUppureem ne tibſees/ bet few paſchu labbis\nPrahtis nodohjees: 7/ etc. Un tahdu Lab-\nbadarrischann zaur to Ewangeljumu eekſch\nwiſas Paſaules isplattibs: 10 etc.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eena Dahwida Dseef-\nma/ preeſch ta augsta\nDseedataja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es gaidu gatdidams us to\nKUNGU/ wiſch greeschahs pee\nmannim/ un paklausfa mannu\nKleegſchanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo wiſch iſwikſe manni\nno tahs breetnigas Bedres/ un\nno tahm dublainahm Duhrnahm/\nun eczhle mannas Kabjas us\nAkmiha-Kalnu/ un ſtiprinaja\nmannus Sohtus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un irr man januu Dseef-\nmu Mutte lizzis/ weenu teiza-\nnu Dseefmu preeſch muhſit\nDeewu/ daudsto redſehs un bih-\nſees/ un zerrehs us to KUNGU.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Swehtigs irr tas Wihrs/\nkas us to KUNGU faru Zerri-\nbu leek/ un ne greeschahs us Lep-\nneem/ un kas ar Melleem tin-\nnahs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "KUNGS mans Deews!\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
